## /commit
Stage all modified tracked files, run typecheck, then commit with a proper message.
Steps:
1. Run typecheck — stop and fix errors if any
2. `git -C /Users/anton/Documents/fundcalm status`
3. `git -C /Users/anton/Documents/fundcalm diff --stat HEAD`
4. Stage relevant files (never .env, never settings.local.json)
5. Write commit: imperative title + blank line + detail bullets + Co-Authored-By trailer
6. Push to origin main

